text: Emilio Lecuona (30 August 1935 - 12 February 2004) was a Spanish gymnast. He competed in eight events at the 1960 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1935 births Category:2004 deaths Category:Spanish male artistic gymnasts Category:Olympic gymnasts of Spain Category:Gymnasts at the 1960 Summer Olympics Category:Gymnasts from Barcelona
